{"tid":1299737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［表揚］點解冇咩人提科技罪案既莫俊傑警司","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T20:51:48.000Z","uid":166886,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5e019f6361df8d194cb2e51013af4c5311efc7","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:47:57.000Z","msg":"陶輝同莊定賢都衣錦還鄉啦，點解冇咩人提呢位抽出起警察底暴徒嘅科技罪案調查科警司莫俊傑呢<br />\n有冇巴絲有多啲佢資料，幫幫佢威返返去巴基斯坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Fetb5n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Fetb5n.png&h=90e10159&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgkcDLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgkcDLo.png&h=357cc5cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa386a30b1db4bd89ec490486a33fd68f2055b77","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d58f0b4e88cecba68a17e2e0ca20c1058d32a4d1","tid":1299737,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ecc88f24fd5395ff7ba372b68bc17ce0b5aa65","tid":1299737,"uid":229369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"唔好搞我伙記！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34483f66bcc4b2a927fbd30215eb987d4a131d9","tid":1299737,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15273f795ce38d68e5e3c9aa0915804496a839ea","tid":1299737,"uid":14494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:54:43.000Z","msg":"外國勢力入侵香港"},{"pid":"c0412c5a2446fba7ebe118aa4414954110a5d6d4","tid":1299737,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/UHUIomIf7JM/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FUHUIomIf7JM%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=293b4f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a53d47dda905a6e64b22f22636ba62d59db7dce4","tid":1299737,"uid":49316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"莫俊傑（Mohammed Swalikh Calvin）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b015869f7da292e2d81286902be3b42601bc64c5","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"好感激佢保護警察，警察維持正義點解要俾你哋起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b26091ad6ce5894056463c739b673e5b8f2a68","tid":1299737,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:56:16.000Z","msg":"警方油尖重案組接手調查鳳姐兇殺案，今早油尖警區助理指揮官﹝刑事﹞莫俊傑署理警司在場交代案情。莫SIR原名MohammedSwalikhCalvin，操流利廣東話，是少有的巴基斯坦裔總督察。早於2001年8月，時任中區特別職務隊督察的莫俊傑，負責警方的卧底行動，在中環閣麟街一間SM店舖，搗破地下派對「真人表演」場，目睹不同國籍的好此道者聚首，利用不同的性用品，作出如鞭打、潑蠟及愛撫等行為。最終將店東夫婦及一名女經理拘捕。莫俊傑事後出庭作供稱，行動期間曾親自上門調查。<br />\n<br />\n莫俊傑是運動健將，擅長曲棍球和馬拉松，曾經代表香港曲棍球隊參加2009年的全運會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20150826/54132188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150826%2F54132188&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=417ee817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150826%2F54132188&h=5b158a31\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20150826/54132188</a>"},{"pid":"bc13f604823bff7eafc7149d9ffb0dfe48bcb1a0","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:56:42.000Z","msg":"曾破10式SM真人騷南亞督察做卧底<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20150826/54132188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150826%2F54132188&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=417ee817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150826%2F54132188&h=5b158a31\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20150826/54132188</a><br />\n幾時落屯公放蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7de13838cd18840e2e7cf93622f421af515251","tid":1299737,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20150826/large/1440568736_da6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20150826%2Flarge%2F1440568736_da6c.jpg&h=fa5dcd34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad0cac80b3893ed3286f1bd6b7016e724b4311b","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"補返莫sir豐功偉績先<br />\n<br />\n網罪科熱線收800警舉報 150宗轉介私隱署<br />\n<br />\n近日有人網上發布警員資料，網罪科拘捕7男2女，他們介乎16至40歲，涉不誠實取用電腦、刑事毁壞等罪行，警方不排除有進一步拘捕行動。網罪科警司莫俊傑說，網罪科熱線收到逾800名警員舉報，其中涉警員及家人中英文全名、身分證號碼、住址等資料被公開，有警員收到大量滋擾電話及恐嚇短訊，另有警員家屬遭恐嚇。其中150宗個案已轉介私隱專員公署。<br />\n<br />\n莫俊傑稱，警方偵測到有人發動DDoS攻擊警方網站但不果，一人涉刑毁被捕。另一人涉多次嘗試登入警方內聯網，涉不誠實使用電腦。消息稱，4人涉網上起底，干犯《私隱條例》第64條披露未經資料使用者同意而取得的個人資料，其中一人設網站大規模披露警員資料。兩人在討論區及Telegram發布有關使用汽油彈或炸彈攻擊警車、警署或其他政府部門的言論，涉觸犯《刑事罪行條例》第61條威脅會摧毁或損壞財產，據悉包括一名梁姓小學教師。莫俊傑強調網絡世界非無法可依。餘下一人詳情未知。<br />\n<br />\n警消息：正蒐證 不會一次過拘捕<br />\n<br />\n對於會否大搜捕，警方消息人士說警方正在蒐證，每宗個案一有足夠證據便會拘捕，<span style=\"color: red;\">故不會出現一次過拘捕行動</span>。他說過去多次衝擊或包圍，激進示威者的暴力程度一次比一次嚴重，警方必須發出信息，即涉暴力者必被追究，否則會令暴力升級，「示威者會以為做了幾次都無事，下次再激一點」。<br />\n<br />\n重識得玩埋白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562177421555/七一衝突拘13人-最細14歲-另9人涉「起底」等網罪被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562177421555%2F%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%8B%9813%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B014%E6%AD%B2-%E5%8F%A69%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E3%80%8D%E7%AD%89%E7%B6%B2%E7%BD%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=7d6b4c97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190704%2Fs00001%2F1562177421555%2F%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E6%8B%9813%E4%BA%BA-%E6%9C%80%E7%B4%B014%E6%AD%B2-%E5%8F%A69%E4%BA%BA%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95%E3%80%8D%E7%AD%89%E7%B6%B2%E7%BD%AA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&h=9488e3df\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/要聞/article/20190704/s00001/1562177421555/七一衝突拘13人-最細14歲-另9人涉「起底」等網罪被捕</a>"},{"pid":"4075f9551d44c0072f2711e1c70ad90f3c3e6895","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"唔知莫sir去開邊間清真寺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUst南亞仔去鳩咗邊"},{"pid":"682f4bbab3c6828ac8014bbe3501705966689f1f","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4795407cbe0d57f61d2c1cf0c8a0cd2f65f03ebb","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"莫sir，可唔可以為同胞發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦在2018年起成為中國大陸婚姻經紀人的焦點，以發大財、過上好生活為賣點，吸引1000多名巴基斯坦婦女與中國男人結婚，不料，這些婦女卻成為人蛇集團的賣淫工具，被帶到中國後，遭到中國男子集體性侵。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，巴基斯坦官員試圖破獲人口販賣集團，並證實有許多貧困的巴基斯坦人將女兒嫁給中國男子，以換取大量現金，但這些女性最後都被迫在中國賣淫。一名官員匿名表示，他們相信大部分的女性都是假結婚、真賣淫的方式被出售的。<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n《美聯社》採訪7名受害的巴基斯坦婦女，一名婦女蘇瑪拉（Sumaira）說，她被兄弟賣給中國男子，強迫她結婚，當時仍在巴基斯坦，丈夫就將她關在一間房間內，整整一個星期都遭到中國男子集體性侵。她氣得質問她的兄弟「你為什麼賣我？你賣我拿了多少錢？」但最後被兄弟毆打，她則逃到叔叔家。<br />\n▼影片取自YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n另一名20歲的娜塔莎瑪西（Natasha Masih）完全公開自己長相，挺身而出講述自己悲慘的遭遇。瑪西說，她與中國丈夫結婚後，就被藏在一間偏鄉的房子內，丈夫讓其他中國男子付錢並性侵她，或是將她帶到酒店賣淫，她被迫成為性奴，甚至挨罵：「我在巴基斯坦買了妳，妳屬於我，妳是我的財產。」<br />\n直到瑪西打電話給父母，並向教會求救，才找到一名在中國讀書的巴基斯坦男人，偽裝成嫖客，趁著在酒店交易時帶走瑪西，讓瑪西搭上回巴基斯坦的飛機，成功解救了她。<br />\n不過瑪西表示，還有許多巴基斯坦婦女仍被迫賣淫，希望未來不要再有巴基斯坦婦女被中國騙婚，「我很幸運，還有很多被丈夫帶到中國的女孩仍過著可怕的生活，現在我知道什麼是自由、什麼是奴隸，在中國，我被丈夫視為奴隸。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190620/1471207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190620%2F1471207.htm&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1dKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=cbc7c5a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190620/1471207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b5d0ab11fb12997cfaf7df8d1dd48ba51b59f307","tid":1299737,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"狗"},{"pid":"8e2507cb2b6b8e04e29ef9cd191804a281a4bd32","tid":1299737,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"係穆罕默德"},{"pid":"982d3ea57628bd7150498703ddfb6791e0ffc55e","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69fb03ea015b036239a70a6d69f2c616f4db880f","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c71c4e42d555cf4325a0e3748c7fda37ad2c2337","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d410ac42ac85577f3601690514cfb104cdb3f9e0","tid":1299737,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4075f9551d44c0072f2711e1c70ad90f3c3e6895","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"唔知莫sir去開邊間清真寺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUst南亞仔去鳩咗邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"我錫克教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f890b24b2bec578454e484a7f93181ad204a0f5","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d410ac42ac85577f3601690514cfb104cdb3f9e0","tid":1299737,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4075f9551d44c0072f2711e1c70ad90f3c3e6895","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"唔知莫sir去開邊間清真寺呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUst南亞仔去鳩咗邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"我錫克教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:39:13.000Z","msg":"大頭綠衣吹bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb3fe09632e97f07327cf554c1b95a19c8ae272","tid":1299737,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f5d5ed42cbf6b42de48e15e927b3a5948ef1b9","tid":1299737,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"莫sir教madam唔帶頭巾短䄂入清真寺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴清真寺昨日受到警方水炮車噴射藍色水劑影響。巴基斯坦裔、網絡安全及科技罪案調查科警司莫俊傑，回應宗教敏感度問題，指警方已經即刻澄清，警方並無惡意，並非去冒犯任何宗教，澄清水炮車水劑不是直接射中清真寺，只是影響了清真寺門口及大閘。<br />\n<br />\n他指，明白有穆斯林覺得不滿意，警方真誠表達歉意。他又澄清，警方並非事發後7小時才道歉，警方已經立即聯絡九龍清真寺首席教長及穆斯林團體，有警察義工亦提出希望到場清理，但昨日傍晚現場並不安全，清真寺也認為當時不是適合時機進行清理。直至昨晚情況許可警方油尖警區人員、公共關係科及他本人親自到清真寺清理及解釋。<br />\n<br />\n莫俊傑指，有意見認為警方不尊重少數族群或宗教，網上迅速已經炒作，甚至形容是直接針對清真寺、要向全球穆斯林宣戰、要穆斯林發動「聖戰」。他批評這些人散播仇恨，強調穆斯林群體都是和平理性一群，不是講求仇恨或報復。警員親身去清理及解釋，九龍清真寺及穆斯林領袖接受警方的歉意及尊重。<br />\n<br />\n對於公共關係科高級警司余鎧均昨晚到清真寺時穿短袖上衣，莫俊傑解釋，根據伊斯蘭規定，《可蘭經》要求女士遮蔽下體及胸部，到場女警不是穆斯林，而且一切衣著言行舉止都非常尊重，不是進入信徒祈禱場所，去的都是辦公地方。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------<br />\n<br />\n原來可蘭經淨係要求女士遮下體同胸部，咁madam下次係咪可以着三點式？<br />\n原來只有祈禱場所先算清真寺<br />\n原來停低瞄準大門射係保護清真寺<br />\n莫sir跟開邊位長老？<br />\n<br />\n真係唔該南亞巴絲將莫sir提倡既新教義傳一傳返去俾巴基斯坦"}]}